px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-5-things-to-know-before-creating-a-blog\">5 Things to know before creating a blog<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\u2019s do a quick stop before we hit the road. Here are 5 important things you must know before creating that blog. You can call this blogging 101.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-a-niche-or-a-personality-is-important\"><strong><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-35  alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blog-Niche-300x200.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 203px) 100vw, 203px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blog-Niche-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blog-Niche-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blog-Niche.jpg 1000w\" alt=\"\" width=\"203\" height=\"135\">A niche or a personality is important<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are hundreds of thousands of other blogs out there that will compete for your proposed audience. You might want to first pause, and do a quick brainstorming on what problem you want to solve and how you want to sound to your audience. You might want to give your blog a personality that sticks, a name to remember, and a niche to demand. In simple terms, plan to be different.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-33 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Precision-296x300.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 191px) 100vw, 191px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Precision-296x300.png 296w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Precision-768x780.png 768w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Precision.png 860w\" alt=\"Simple and precise posts\" width=\"191\" height=\"194\"><\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-don-t-overdo-it-be-simple-and-precise\"><strong>Don\u2019t overdo it. Be simple and precise<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Not everyone loves going round and round in suspense. Be simple, direct, and precise. You shouldn\u2019t always think the longer your post will be, the better. The secret is to make them interesting, engaging and resourceful. You can make a list of what you hope to communicate and get them passed to the reader in the simplest possible way you know.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-\">&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-consistency-is-of-great-advantage\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-36 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blog-titles-300x300.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 194px) 100vw, 194px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blog-titles-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blog-titles-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blog-titles.jpg 450w\" alt=\"Blog consistency is important\" width=\"194\" height=\"194\">Consistency is of great advantage <\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here is an important key for building an effective blog. Employ the power of consistency.&nbsp;It\u2019s important to ensure your post are regular and on time, to meet the desires and interests of your readers. Now, you don\u2019t want to always keep your readers waiting. Consistency is how they know they can trust you. Win their trust with consistency.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h--1\">&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-titles-are-your-first-impressions\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-34 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Title-300x180.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 201px) 100vw, 201px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Title-300x180.png 300w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Title-1024x614.png 1024w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Title-768x461.png 768w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Title.png 1200w\" alt=\"Blog tittles draw attention\" width=\"201\" height=\"121\">Titles are your first impressions<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Titles are important. They make or mar your articles and posts. They draw traffic and capture the attention of your target readers. Always keep it short, catchy, interesting, actionable, and consisting of your keywords. You might want to check out the title of this post for a clue. You can put in one or two call-to-action to motivate an interest to read your article.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-your-readers-deserve-a-voice-too\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-37 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Comments-300x240.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 204px) 100vw, 204px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Comments-300x240.jpg 300w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Comments.jpg 626w\" alt=\"the importance of Comments in blogs\" width=\"204\" height=\"163\">Your readers deserve a voice too<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Don\u2019t just write to your readers, allow your readers to write to you too. Make room for comments and suggestions. Make the communication two-way traffic. Allow comments on your articles and make room to reply to them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"832\" height=\"575\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/111773543_s.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-24\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/111773543_s.jpg 832w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/111773543_s-300x207.jpg 300w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/111773543_s-768x531.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 832px) 100vw, 832px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-steps-for-building-an-effective-blog\">STEPS FOR BUILDING AN EFFECTIVE BLOG<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Good work! We\u2019re almost there. With the basic foundational knowledge for designing a blog, things are sure to go awesome for you. Now that you know these, let\u2019s get your blog running, shall we? To build an effective blog, you should follow the steps below:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-identify-a-passion-or-niche-you-want-to-focus-on\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-43 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/blog-niche-ideas-300x150.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 228px) 100vw, 228px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/blog-niche-ideas-300x150.png 300w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/blog-niche-ideas-768x384.png 768w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/blog-niche-ideas.png 800w\" alt=\"Choosing your blog niche\" width=\"228\" height=\"114\">Identify a passion or niche you want to focus on<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This could be fashion, music, religion, culinary, health and wellness, sports etc. It is important to love what you want to focus on and blog about. Your passion will be tested with time. You can get awesome ideas from my article on the <a href=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/best-niche-for-blogging-140-best-blog-niche-ideas-to-choose-from\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">best niche for blogging with 140 best blog niche ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-decide-on-a-name-naming-is-important-for-designing-a-blog\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"asy