">Get web hosting and install WordPress or create an account with wordpress.com.<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You should install a theme and stick to it. Next, customize your blog to accommodate the type of content you hope to write. You can get this done by clicking on Customize button on your WordPress.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-optimize-your-blog\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-38 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blogging-1-680x380-min-300x168.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 220px) 100vw, 220px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blogging-1-680x380-min-300x168.png 300w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Blogging-1-680x380-min.png 680w\" alt=\"Optimizing a blog\" width=\"220\" height=\"123\">Optimize your blog<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Incorporate good Search Engine Optimization (SEO) on your blog. Install plugins, forms and other features that will help your blogs rank high in searches and help build an awesome user experience for your readers. A good plugin for SEO is Yoast SEO.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-prepare-a-list-of-topics-you-would-like-to-write-on\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-42 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Research-you-post-300x193.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Research-you-post-300x193.jpg 300w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Research-you-post.jpg 768w\" alt=\"Content reserch\" width=\"225\" height=\"145\">Prepare a list of topics you would like to write on<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This is one of the most important of learning how to build a blog. Your content must be on-demand. Ensure they are things your target audience would love to read. Research your topics carefully and ensure they are resourceful and would be useful to the readers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-go-ahead-and-make-your-first-post\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-45 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Writing-a-post-300x195.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Writing-a-post-300x195.png 300w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Writing-a-post-768x499.png 768w, https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Writing-a-post.png 1000w\" alt=\"How to write a blog post\" width=\"300\" height=\"195\">Go ahead and make your first post<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>With a list of topics ready to go, now it\u2019s time to create your first post. Try writing from your heart. Use engaging communication styles to connect with your audience, don\u2019t be too formal. Make your posts nice and easy, simple and precise. It is important to add pictures and images to your post to draw the attention of the readers too. See where you can get <a href=\"https:\/\/highblogtraffic.com\/finally-revealed-20-websites-to-get-free-images-for-blogs-and-graphic-designs\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">free images for blogs<\/a> in my article.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With your first post gone live and published, you are good to go. It is important to follow up on comments from your readers in the comment section and look out for corrections and editions on your post as you keep on researching the topics you\u2019ve written on.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>How about you leave a comment and let me know how helpful this is in building an effective blog for you? I\u2019d be glad to read from you too in a bit.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If you\u2019ve always wanted to build and own an effective blog with high blog traffic, then you are not alone&#8230;.